GEM.SYS is the lastest multitasking GEM from Atari Corp. It was
released as beta version with the MultiTOS 1.08beta altogether.

ATTENTION: You have to know and realize that this AES works, but is slow. 
If you want the maximum compatibility and a way faster AES get N_AES.
Commercial, but it really rocks and worths the money. 

